<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 zhè shì qí miào de shì, zhè shì xī qí de shì,
 wǒ men jīn tiān xiāng jù zài yī qǐ. zhǔ zài wǒ men zhōng jiān.
 wǒ men hé děng miǎo xiǎo, wǒ men hé děng bēi wēi.
 chuàng zào de zhǔ jìng hé wǒ men tóng gōng, hé wǒ men yǒng xiāng suí.
 ràng wǒ men jǔ qǐ shǒu, ràng wǒ men zhāng kāi kǒu,
 xiàng yǒng shēng shén xiàn shàng gǎn xiè, shì cóng nèi xīn fā chū.</lyrics>
<title>zhè shì qí miào de shì 迦南717</title>
<hymn_number>717</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>